{"tid":614423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日發生6宗行山中暑或受傷個案 及3宗行山迷路報案 飛行服務隊頻出動","createTime":"2018-04-02T13:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T13:46:44.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8919351dc6d2a535020cd8f24c9727fe5d43b3a7","tid":614423,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"今日全日發生至少6宗行山中暑或受傷的事故，以及3宗中途迷路求助的報案。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180402&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58024817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180402%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58024817&d=6NjUVdMNZjxvOCxuEg%2FSzKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d1e141f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180402%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58024817&h=b3129cc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180402&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58024817</a><br />\n<br />\n今日是復活節最後一天假期，天清氣爽，不少港人選擇出遊遠足，惟全日發生至少6宗行山中暑或受傷的事故，以及3宗中途迷路求助的報案，政府飛行服務共出動4次飛抵現場救人，當中一名56歲女行山客偕友人挑戰五星難度的西貢蚺蛇尖時失足跌倒，頭部受傷送往東區醫院敷治，另有5名男女亦須送院。"},{"pid":"7ce3300537e491d63ed8fe3f2f2cefc135144b32","tid":614423,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}